The paper deals with the detection of forged images and videos, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning techniques such as capsule networks is also a key aspect of the paper, which suggests that it could also be relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.MM), cryptography and security (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and learning (cs.LG).
